WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
The check-in, reinvented — a production member check-in platform, designed and built solo.

00:07.000 --> 00:18.000
The old way: every visit started with a form. Manual entry at the front desk, keystroke by keystroke. Too slow.

00:18.000 --> 00:33.000
The new way: one scan, zero typing. Scan a license and the member is checked in.

00:33.000 --> 00:43.000
Head to head — seconds, not minutes. Average peak-hour check-in time fell 50%.

00:43.000 --> 00:55.000
Plays nice with Square. Memberships, transactions and check-ins stay in sync. No double entry.

00:55.000 --> 01:06.000
For the staff: the front desk sees everything — a live arrivals view.

01:06.000 --> 01:11.000
Under the hood: enterprise habits, startup speed. TypeScript, Next.js, Postgres, and an AAMVA barcode pipeline.

01:11.000 --> 01:20.000
One engineer. Full production value.
